{"tid":1383293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(多方面文宣) 大家得閒推下罷工POST 但唔好剩係推POST","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:09.000Z","uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adcad99ee94eb99e3bf850bf2fef9d58b3ff23ca","tid":1383293,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"唔該得閒推下罷工POST 個人認為8月5日既罷工係好重要 可以既話要無限期罷落去<br />\n<br />\n另外唔知係咪好多人覺得推左POST就當做左文宣  我覺得要整個文宣攻略<br />\n唔該 至少COPY多幾次LINK去Facebook Twitter IG 剩係連登推就只會得連登仔知<br />\ne.g. 主題主要都係警黑勾結, 中聯辦治港, 黑警開槍鎮壓, 元朗恐襲, 各位再加<br />\nFacebook: like, share, post<br />\nTwitter: hashtag, like, retweet, share<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得已經死左幾位烈士 係死左...呢世都見唔返佢地... 佢既<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>雨衣 佢既背影...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工啦 好嗎??</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/1D77/production/_107834570_hi054670827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F1D77%2Fproduction%2F_107834570_hi054670827.jpg&h=16f999e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suBetSU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBetSU.png&h=e982f870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/379PhMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F379PhMe.png&h=a552423d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a44597471a9d5dad374867f9dcacce5dbc1620e","tid":1383293,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed6fbbea4f6938beec6dca914cb3d5c368e70f9","tid":1383293,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:19:24.000Z","msg